Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1233 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor"

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1312 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1330 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1337 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1337 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1357 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1357 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1394 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1394 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1401 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1401 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1410 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1410 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1418 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1426 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1426 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1432 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1444 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1503 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1503 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1510 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1510 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 1520 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor"

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 112 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 164 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL

                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor"

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 3792 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 4602 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
