Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 5058 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 5745 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor"

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 6758 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 6758 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 6778 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7001 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7104 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7104 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7188 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7246 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7291 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7291 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
