Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7299 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7310 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7349 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7367 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7386 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7410 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7410 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20")

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7420 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7427 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7434 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7453 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7453 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 6 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                6 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 7481 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 6
                                        UNION ALL

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                4 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100002 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100002 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                100002 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=2 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 100002
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)
                                        ) x  UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 2 AS "Index", IdUser, -4 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -4) AND IdUser = 100002
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -4)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 2 AS "F10003", 22 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2019-12-03') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2019-12-03') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "IdStare", 4 AS "IdCircuit", 100002 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", 0.5 AS "NrOre", NULL AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,null  AS "CampExtra6" ,null  AS "CampExtra7" ,null  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" ; COMMIT TRAN

                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 15 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 9 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 9 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME)

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                3 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                3 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2550 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 3
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2550 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 2550 AS "F10003", 1 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2020-02-19') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2020-02-19') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "IdStare", 3 AS "IdCircuit", 3 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", NULL AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", 0 AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,'211'  AS "CampExtra6" ,'211'  AS "CampExtra7" ,'Nu'  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" , 3 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, null AS "IdCerereDivizata", null AS "Comentarii", 0 AS "CampBifa"; COMMIT TRAN

                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare",

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                100012 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=100012 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 2 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 100012 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 100012
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 100012 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit",  "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 100012 AS "F10003", 19 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2020-06-03') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2020-06-03') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "IdStare", 1 AS "IdCircuit", 100012 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", 4 AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", NULL AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,null  AS "CampExtra6" ,null  AS "CampExtra7" ,null  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" ; COMMIT TRAN

                                3 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat",

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                3 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                3 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2734 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 3
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2734 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa")

                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                4 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare",

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                74 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=110 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 37
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 110 AS "F10003", 1 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2020-07-29') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2020-07-29') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "IdStare", 74 AS "IdCircuit", 37 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", NULL AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", 0 AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,'43'  AS "CampExtra6" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra7" ,'Nu'  AS "CampExtra8" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" , 37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, null AS "IdCerereDivizata", null AS "Comentarii", 0 AS "CampBifa"; COMMIT TRAN

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                74 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=110 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 37
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 110 AS "F10003", 1 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2020-08-05') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2020-08-05') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "IdStare", 74 AS "IdCircuit", 37 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", NULL AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", 0 AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,'43'  AS "CampExtra6" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra7" ,'Nu'  AS "CampExtra8" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" , 37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, null AS "IdCerereDivizata", null AS "Comentarii", 0 AS "CampBifa"; COMMIT TRAN

Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")

                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                74 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 37 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=110 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 37
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 110 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 110 AS "F10003", 1 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2020-08-11') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2020-08-11') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "IdStare", 74 AS "IdCircuit", 37 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", NULL AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", 0 AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,'43'  AS "CampExtra6" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra7" ,'Nu'  AS "CampExtra8" ,'25'  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" , 37 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, null AS "IdCerereDivizata", null AS "Comentarii", 0 AS "CampBifa"; COMMIT TRAN

                                "IdUser",

                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 2 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                2 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 173 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 2  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2020-12-18') AND CONVERT(date,'2020-12-18') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 173 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2020-12-18') AND CONVERT(date,'2020-12-18') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20", USER_NO, TIME, "IdCerereDivizata", "Comentarii", "CampBifa")

                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT 8001 AS "IdCerere", 
                                3 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                3 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (

                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 3 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                3 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT TOP 1 0 AS "Index", IdUser, -3 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2550 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3) AND IdUser = 3  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2550 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -3)  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit", "AreAtas","IdCerereDivizata", USER_NO, TIME, "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT 8089 AS "Id",2550 AS "F10003",1 AS "IdAbsenta",CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') AS "DataInceput",CONVERT(date,'2021-03-25') AS "DataSfarsit",1 AS "NrZile",NULL AS "NrZileViitor",'''Day off - Women''s Day''' AS "Observatii",(SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=8089 ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "IdStare",3 AS "IdCircuit",3 AS "UserIntrod",(SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=8089 ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Culoare",NULL AS "Inlocuitor",(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=8089) AS "TotalSuperCircuit",(SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=8089 ORDER BY "Pozitie" DESC)  AS "Pozitie",NULL AS "TrimiteLa",NULL AS "NrOre",NULL AS "OraInceput",NULL AS "OraSfarsit",0 AS "AreAtas",NULL AS "IdCerereDivizata",3 AS "USER_NO",GetDate() AS "TIME",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,(SELECT RAMASE FROM SITUATIEZILEABSENTE WHERE F10003=2550 AND AN=YEAR(CONVERT(DATE,'2021-03-25')))  AS "CampExtra6" ,(SELECT RAMASEDEPLANIFICAT FROM SITUATIEZILEABSENTE WHERE F10003=2550 AND AN=YEAR(CONVERT(DATE,'2021-03-25')))  AS "CampExtra7" ,'Nu'  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" ; COMMIT TRAN
