Select:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100012 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                100012 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=100012 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -1 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 100012 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -1) AND IdUser = 100012  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 100012 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -1)  AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') AND CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') <= "DataSfarsit"  
                                        ) x ) W) X) G; INSERT INTO "Ptj_Cereri"("Id", F10003, "IdAbsenta", "DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile", "NrZileViitor", "Observatii", "IdStare", "IdCircuit", "UserIntrod", "Culoare", "Inlocuitor", "TotalSuperCircuit", "Pozitie", "TrimiteLa", "NrOre", "OraInceput", "OraSfarsit",  "AreAtas", "CampExtra1", "CampExtra2", "CampExtra3", "CampExtra4", "CampExtra5", "CampExtra6", "CampExtra7", "CampExtra8", "CampExtra9", "CampExtra10", "CampExtra11", "CampExtra12", "CampExtra13", "CampExtra14", "CampExtra15", "CampExtra16", "CampExtra17", "CampExtra18", "CampExtra19", "CampExtra20") 
                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "Id", 100012 AS "F10003", 1 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2021-04-21') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")) AS "IdStare", 1 AS "IdCircuit", 100012 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")) AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")) AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", NULL AS "NrOre", NULL AS "OraInceput", NULL AS "OraSfarsit", NULL AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,null  AS "CampExtra6" ,null  AS "CampExtra7" ,null  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" ; COMMIT TRAN

                                79 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE

                                1 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser",

                                3 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (1 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE
